# Homelab DNS source-of-truth on OpenWrt
#
# Role:
# - Resolve home.arpa local device/module names.
# - OpenWrt should become the primary DNS source-of-truth.
#
# Format:
# IP    FQDN aliases...


# ===== OpenWrt / Gateways =====
192.168.10.1    openwrt.home.arpa openwrt infra-gw.home.arpa infra-gw vlan10-gw
192.168.31.1    openwrt-legacy.home.arpa openwrt-legacy legacy-gw.home.arpa legacy-gw
192.168.30.1    storage-gw.home.arpa storage-gw vlan30-gw
192.168.40.1    trusted-gw.home.arpa trusted-gw vlan40-gw
192.168.50.1    iot-gw.home.arpa iot-gw vlan50-gw
10.60.60.1      dmz-gw.home.arpa dmz-gw vlan60-gw
10.67.67.1      game-gw.home.arpa game-gw vlan67-gw
10.80.80.1      service-gw.home.arpa service-gw monitor-gw.home.arpa vlan80-gw
10.66.66.1      honeypot-gw.home.arpa honeypot-gw vlan666-gw

# ===== Router PVE / N95 =====
